Summary: I was unaware it was even there at the moment
divs: Sighting Details(1)I was at Summerlea Park with my friend and he told me to take some pictures of his as we worked out at the playground to be posted on facebook. (2)After I returned home I noticed this disk-shaped object just above the pyramid observation post of West Edmonton Mall. (3)That looked weird to me so that's why I'm submitting it to you. (4)Unknown, but it didn't appear in the rest of the pictures we've taken, even though at least 2 pictures showed a similar angle. (5)Intrigued, surprised, excited, etc. (6)See above reasoning.
